# 1. Executive Summary

SmartSupply AI is a cloud-native, multi-tenant B2B SaaS platform that serves as the operating system for retail supply chains. It connects retailers (kirana stores, pharmacies, hardware stores, grocery stores, electronics stores), wholesalers, distributors, manufacturers, and delivery partners into a unified ecosystem.

The platform provides real-time inventory visibility, AI-powered demand forecasting, intelligent procurement automation, supplier marketplace, multi-channel notifications, and comprehensive business analytics — enabling every retailer to procure the right products, at the right time, from the right supplier, at the best price.

SmartSupply AI eliminates inventory mismanagement, reduces stockouts by up to 80%, minimizes dead inventory by 60%, improves cash flow by 25%, and increases retailer profitability by 15-30%.

