### Direct Competitors

| Competitor | Strengths | Weaknesses | SmartSupply AI Advantage |
|-----------|-----------|------------|------------------------|
| **Udaan** | Large marketplace, logistics | No inventory management, no forecasting | Integrated inventory + marketplace + AI |
